===Proper noun===
'''Nevada'''

#A {{USstate}} Capital: [[Carson City]].

===Pronunciation===
<!-- Not sure if /ʌ/ is the right vowel.  English vowels are confusing. -->
Typically pronounced /nʌ'vɑdɑ/ by non-residents, /nʌ'vædɑ/ by residents.  (Residents often regard the pronunciation as a test of whether visitors, such as presidential candidates, have informed themselves about the state.)

